{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_01_03",
  "title": "川咲さくら 3話 やりたかったこと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ、{user}さん\nお疲れさまです。出かけるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san…\nThank you for your hard work. Are you heading out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.754480759302776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、仕事が一段落したし\nちょっと浜辺まで散歩でもしようと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ work’s calmed down a bit‚\nso I thought I’d take a stroll on the shore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.710340213775636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.124830055236817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、それなら私もついていっていいですか？\n浜辺に行くなら集めたいものがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ so would it be okay for me to go with you?\nIf we’re going to the shore‚ there are some things I’d like to collect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.591496721903486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_lesson_noon",
      "startTime": 19.824830055236824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "あっ！　さっそく見つけました～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah! I found some already!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.224830055236826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "これ、色が可愛い！　こっちは形がハートみたい……\nほら、見て下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This one has a cute color! And that one’s shaped like a heart.\nHey‚ look at this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.72483015060426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "貝殻なんて集めてどうするんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What will you do with the shells after you collect them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.327105912295266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ボトルインテリアを作ってみようかなって思って\n小さい瓶の中に、きれいな砂と一緒に入れて飾るんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I’d make an ornamental bottle.\nI could put the shells together with some pretty sand inside a small bottle for decoration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.45247995925675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "あと、大きな貝殻ならキャンドルスタンドとか\n写真立ての飾り付けとか、いろいろ使えますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I could use big shells to make a candle holder or something‚\nor to decorate a picture frame. There are lots of ways to use them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.38865022275007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "へえ……凄いな\nさくらはそういう工作が好きなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… that’s impressive.\nSo you like handicraft‚ Sakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.30315131756819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "好き……って聞かれると、ちょっと違うかな？\nやってみたかった、って方が近いと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… I guess I won’t exactly call it “like.”\nIt’s more that I wanted to try it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.73843199288502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "テレビでやってて可愛いなぁ、おしゃれだなぁ……\nって思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw it done on TV and thought it was cute…\n…and cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.59369077445845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、いろいろありますよ？\n退院したらやってみたかったリスト！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve got lots of other stuff that I want to try out.\nI’ve got a list of things to try after I got out of the hospital!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.13985765910924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "例えば……スキー、スノーボードとか\nダイビングに登山、あとボルダリングとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For example‚ skiing‚ snowboarding‚\ndiving‚ mountain climbing‚ and bouldering…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.33520756057521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "けっこうアクティブなものが多いんだな\n元気なさくららしいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a lot of pretty outdoor stuff.\nThat’s just like the healthy Sakura that you are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.18683512972416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは\nそういうやってみたいことって何かありますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\ndo you have something you want to try?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7408581905776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それはもちろん\nみんなをトップアイドルに導くことだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nI want to lead all of you to become top idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.33775659559116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "あはは\n{user}さんらしいっていうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha.\nThat’s just like you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.87191167829384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんだからこその\n「普通」って感じですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It sounded so normal‚ {user}-san.\nBecause it’s just what you’d say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.65847522990605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "そういうの、素敵だなって思います\n私は……「普通」になれなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think that’s a wonderful thing.\nBecause I… couldn’t get to be “normal.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.22418864823088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが当たり前にしていることが全然出来なくて\nずっとテレビを見たりして、辛いのをごまかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never had the chance to do things that were totally natural for everyone else.\nI was always watching TV and pretending to be happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.54085536402616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "でも画面の向こうの世界を知れば知るほど\nやっぱり辛くて……それに、悔しかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the more I learned about the world on the other side of the screen‚\nthe more painful it was‚ and bitter as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.25941975871328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "悔しい……か\n入院を余儀なくされたら、そう思いたくなるよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bitter…?\nWhen you have to be hospitalized‚ I guess you can’t help but feel that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.69275309204673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "びっくりでしたよ\n急にいろんなことが出来なくなっちゃいましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a shock.\nSuddenly‚ there were so many things I couldn’t do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.32608642538003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "あれもダメ、これもダメで入院期間は長引くし……\n早く良くならないかな～って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This was out‚ that was out‚ and my time in hospital kept getting longer…\nI thought‚ “couldn’t I just get better quickly?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.2427530920468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "「普通」のことが「普通」に出来ていた自分に\n早く戻りたいなって……思ってばかりだったなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to get back quickly to the person that could do “normal” things like “normal” people.\nThat’s all I could think of.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.8802530920469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……あまり思い出したくないのかなって\n思ってたけど……懐かしむみたいに振り返れるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought maybe you wouldn’t want to remember that stuff‚\nbut you’re looking back like you miss it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.38263024134804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、言われてみれば……なんでなんだろう？\n楽しい思い出って訳じゃ、全然ないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it… why would that be?\nIt’s not like the memories are any fun at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.6894101663766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと乗り越えてるから……じゃないかな？\n病気のことも、入院してたことも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be because you managed to get through it?\nGetting sick and being in hospital.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.13965397712704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_03-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……うん、そうだと思います\n今はもうへっちゃらで、なんでも来い！　ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… Yup‚ I think that’s it.\nNow it’s all cool‚ and I can handle anything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.66064802842445,
